(3, 1, 3, 'Má»¹ Ä‘Æ°a tÃ u khu trá»¥c tÃªn lá»­a dáº«n Ä‘Æ°á»ng tá»›i Ukraine', '&lt;h3&gt;(NLÄO) - T&amp;agrave;u khu trá»¥c t&amp;ecirc;n lá»­a dáº«n Ä‘Æ°á»ng cá»§a Má»¹ USS Ross Ä‘&amp;atilde; cáº­p cáº£ng Odessa cá»§a Ukraine Ä‘á»ƒ tham gia cuá»™c táº­p tráº­n h&amp;agrave;ng háº£i Ä‘a phÆ°Æ¡ng Sea Breeze 2021 á»Ÿ biá»ƒn Äen.&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo Ä‘&amp;agrave;i Sputnik,&amp;nbsp;Trung t&amp;acirc;m Quáº£n l&amp;yacute; Quá»‘c ph&amp;ograve;ng Nga trÆ°á»›c Ä‘&amp;oacute; cho biáº¿t háº£i qu&amp;acirc;n nÆ°á»›c n&amp;agrave;y Ä‘ang theo d&amp;otilde;i t&amp;agrave;u&amp;nbsp;USS Ross sau khi n&amp;oacute; v&amp;agrave;o biá»ƒn Äen ng&amp;agrave;y 26-6.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ng&amp;agrave;y 28-6,&amp;nbsp;t&amp;agrave;u USS Ross Ä‘Æ°á»£c nh&amp;igrave;n tháº¥y cáº­p cáº£ng&amp;nbsp;Odessa cá»§a Ukraine Ä‘á»ƒ chuáº©n bá»‹ tham gia cuá»™c táº­p tráº­n thÆ°á»ng ni&amp;ecirc;n&amp;nbsp;Sea Breeze 2021. Ä&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; láº§n thá»©&amp;nbsp;21 cuá»™c táº­p tráº­n n&amp;agrave;y Ä‘Æ°á»£c tá»• chá»©c. Lá»±c lÆ°á»£ng Ä‘áº¿n tá»« hÆ¡n&amp;nbsp;30 quá»‘c gia sáº½ tham gia Ä‘&amp;agrave;o táº¡o kháº£ nÄƒng tÆ°Æ¡ng t&amp;aacute;c á»Ÿ biá»ƒn Äen.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Cuá»™c táº­p tráº­n&amp;nbsp;Sea Breeze nÄƒm nay dá»± kiáº¿n k&amp;eacute;o d&amp;agrave;i 13 ng&amp;agrave;y,&amp;nbsp;khá»Ÿi Ä‘á»™ng v&amp;agrave;o ng&amp;agrave;y 28-6. Khoáº£ng 5.000 qu&amp;acirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n v&amp;agrave; hÆ¡n 30 t&amp;agrave;u tá»« Má»¹, Ukraine, Anh, Canada, H&amp;agrave; Lan, Bulgaria, Hy Láº¡p, Latvia v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c quá»‘c gia kh&amp;aacute;c sáº½ tham dá»±.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://nld.mediacdn.vn/thumb_w/684/291774122806476800/2021/6/28/1-16248768237741867370587.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:318px; width:500px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https:/