(4, 1, 24, 'DÃ²ng tiá»n quay láº¡i chá»©ng khoÃ¡n, VN-Index trá»¥ vá»¯ng má»‘c 1.400 Ä‘iá»ƒm', '&lt;h3&gt;(NLÄO) - Ä&amp;oacute;ng cá»­a phi&amp;ecirc;n giao dá»‹ch chá»©ng kho&amp;aacute;n Ä‘áº§u tuáº§n (28-6), nh&amp;agrave; Ä‘áº§u tÆ° hÆ°ng pháº¥n khi VN-Index Ä‘&amp;atilde; trá»¥ vá»¯ng má»©c 1.400 Ä‘iá»ƒm, Ä‘á»“ng thá»i gi&amp;aacute; trá»‹ giao dá»‹ch cÅ©ng tÄƒng cao so vá»›i nhá»¯ng phi&amp;ecirc;n trÆ°á»›c Ä‘&amp;oacute;.&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Cá»¥ thá»ƒ, káº¿t th&amp;uacute;c ng&amp;agrave;y giao dá»‹ch, VN-Index tÄƒng 15,69 Ä‘iá»ƒm, l&amp;ecirc;n 1.405,81 Ä‘iá»ƒm. Trong khi Ä‘&amp;oacute;, VN30- Index tÄƒng máº¡nh 21,11 Ä‘iá»ƒm, l&amp;ecirc;n 1.521,41 Ä‘iá»ƒm. HNX-Index tÄƒng 4,88 Ä‘iá»ƒm, l&amp;ecirc;n 323,1 Ä‘iá»ƒm. UPCoM-Index cÅ©ng quay Ä‘áº§u tÄƒng nháº¹ 0,32 Ä‘iá»ƒm, l&amp;ecirc;n 89,8 Ä‘iá»ƒm.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ä&amp;aacute;ng ch&amp;uacute; &amp;yacute; phi&amp;ecirc;n n&amp;agrave;y l&amp;agrave; thanh khoáº£n thá»‹ trÆ°á»ng Ä‘&amp;atilde; tÄƒng máº¡nh trá»Ÿ láº¡i, táº¡o t&amp;acirc;m l&amp;yacute; hÆ°ng pháº¥n cho nh&amp;agrave; Ä‘áº§u tÆ° sau 1 tuáº§n giao dá»‹ch giáº£m máº¡nh. Theo Ä‘&amp;oacute;, tá»•ng gi&amp;aacute; trá»‹ giao dá»‹ch to&amp;agrave;n thá»‹ trÆ°á»ng Ä‘áº¡t 27.670 tá»‰ Ä‘á»“ng, tÄƒng kh&amp;aacute; nhiá»u so vá»›i phi&amp;ecirc;n cuá»‘i tuáº§n trÆ°á»›c. Trong Ä‘&amp;oacute;, giao dá»‹ch khá»›p lá»‡nh chiáº¿m 25.800 tá»‰ Ä‘á»“ng ri&amp;ecirc;ng HoSE l&amp;agrave; 21.500 tá»‰ Ä‘á»“ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Máº·c d&amp;ugrave; váº­y, nh&amp;agrave; Ä‘áº§u tÆ° nÆ°á»›c ngo&amp;agrave;i váº«n b&amp;aacute;n r&amp;ograve;ng hÆ¡n 200 tá»‰ Ä‘á»“ng tr&amp;ecirc;n HoSE trong khi mua r&amp;ograve;ng nháº¹ á»Ÿ HNX v&amp;agrave; UPCoM. Trong phi&amp;ecirc;n giao n&amp;agrave;y, c&amp;aacute;c cá»• phiáº¿u ng&amp;agrave;nh t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh, ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng tÄƒng máº¡nh nhÆ° MSB, TPB, TCB, GVR, BVH...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://nld.mediacdn.vn/thumb_w/684/291774122806476800/2021/6/28/img-9473-16248785557291407926861.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:375px; width:500px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong khi Ä‘&amp;oacute;, má»›i má»Ÿ cá»­a thá»‹ trÆ°á»ng, VN-Index Ä‘&amp;atilde; bá»©t ph&amp;aacute; nhÆ°ng khi gáº§n cháº¡m ngÆ°á»¡ng 1.400 Ä‘iá»ƒm th&amp;igrave; giáº±ng co. Sau Ä‘&amp;oacute;, gáº§n cuá»‘i phi&amp;ecirc;n s&amp;aacute;ng má»›i vÆ°á»£t qua ngÆ°á»¡ng 1.400 Ä‘iá»ƒm.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ä&amp;oacute;ng cá»­a phi&amp;ecirc;n s&amp;aacute;ng, VN-Index tÄƒng 12,41 Ä‘iá»ƒm (0,89%) l&amp;ecirc;n 1.402,53 Ä‘iá»ƒm. To&amp;agrave;n s&amp;agrave;n c&amp;oacute; 207 m&amp;atilde; tÄƒng, 177 m&amp;atilde; giáº£m v&amp;agrave; 43 m&amp;atilde; Ä‘á»©ng gi&amp;aacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;HNX-Index cÅ©ng tÄƒng 2,72 Ä‘iá»ƒm (0,85%) l&amp;ecirc;n 320,94 Ä‘iá»ƒm. To&amp;agrave;n s&amp;agrave;n c&amp;oacute; 93 m&amp;atilde; tÄƒng, 103 m&amp;atilde; giáº£m v&amp;agrave; 64 m&amp;atilde; Ä‘á»©ng gi&amp;aacute;. NgÆ°á»£c láº¡i, UPCoM-Index giáº£m 0,12 Ä‘iá»ƒm (-0,13%) xuá»‘ng 89,36 Ä‘iá»ƒm.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nháº­n Ä‘á»‹nh phi&amp;ecirc;n h&amp;ocirc;m nay, &amp;ocirc;ng Huá»³nh Anh Tuáº¥n, Tá»•ng Gi&amp;aacute;m Ä‘á»‘c C&amp;ocirc;ng ty chá»©ng kho&amp;aacute;n Ä&amp;ocirc;ng &amp;Aacute; (DAS), cho ráº±ng vá»›i sá»± thu h&amp;uacute;t d&amp;ograve;ng tiá»n nhÆ° phi&amp;ecirc;n Ä‘áº§u tuáº§n, Ä‘&amp;atilde; k&amp;eacute;o VN-Index l&amp;ecirc;n ngÆ°á»¡ng quan trá»ng 1.400 Ä‘iá»ƒm. Äiá»u n&amp;agrave;y Ä‘&amp;atilde; táº¡o t&amp;acirc;m l&amp;yacute; tá»‘t cho nh&amp;agrave; Ä‘áº§u tÆ°. Äiá»u quan trá»ng l&amp;agrave; káº¿t quáº£ kinh doanh cá»§a c&amp;aacute;c ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng 6 th&amp;aacute;ng Ä‘&amp;atilde; tá»‘t hÆ¡n nÄƒm ngo&amp;aacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Äá»“ng thá»i thá»‹ trÆ°á»ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng chá»‰ táº­p trung v&amp;agrave;o 1 v&amp;agrave;i m&amp;atilde; blueships m&amp;agrave; Ä‘á»“ng loáº¡t tÄƒng gi&amp;aacute; á»Ÿ nhiá»u m&amp;a