á»‹ch thá»© 4, chá»‰ sau Báº¯c Giang (5.663 ca).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Há»p Ban chá»‰ Ä‘áº¡o ph&amp;ograve;ng chá»‘ng Covid-19 cá»§a TP HCM s&amp;aacute;ng 28/6, Gi&amp;aacute;m Ä‘á»‘c Sá»Ÿ Y táº¿ Nguyá»…n Táº¥n Bá»‰nh cho biáº¿t t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh dá»‹ch váº«n diá»…n biáº¿n phá»©c táº¡p. C&amp;aacute;c ca nhiá»…m trong cá»™ng Ä‘á»“ng c&amp;ograve;n gia tÄƒng qua c&amp;aacute;c trÆ°á»ng há»£p c&amp;oacute; triá»‡u chá»©ng Ä‘áº¿n kh&amp;aacute;m á»Ÿ c&amp;aacute;c cÆ¡ sá»Ÿ kh&amp;aacute;m, chá»¯a bá»‡nh (tÄƒng 32-42 ca). Ä&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; nhá»¯ng ca chá»‰ Ä‘iá»ƒm tá»« Ä‘&amp;oacute; tiáº¿n h&amp;agrave;nh truy váº¿t c&amp;aacute;c á»• dá»‹ch á»Ÿ c&amp;aacute;c khu trá», cÆ¡ sá»Ÿ sáº£n xuáº¥t, chá»£ Ä‘áº§u má»‘i...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;TP HCM Ä‘&amp;atilde; chia c&amp;aacute;c quáº­n huyá»‡n th&amp;agrave;nh 3 nh&amp;oacute;m nguy cÆ¡ Ä‘á»ƒ Ä‘Æ°a ra giáº£i ph&amp;aacute;p ph&amp;ograve;ng dá»‹ch. Trong Ä‘&amp;oacute;, nh&amp;oacute;m nguy cÆ¡ ráº¥t cao, gá»“m: B&amp;igrave;nh T&amp;acirc;n, H&amp;oacute;c M&amp;ocirc;n, B&amp;igrave;nh Ch&amp;aacute;nh, quáº­n 8, T&amp;acirc;n Ph&amp;uacute; v&amp;agrave; má»™t pháº§n cá»§a TP Thá»§ Äá»©c (quáº­n Thá»§ Äá»©c cÅ©). Ä&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; nhá»¯ng khu vá»±c ghi nháº­n sá»‘ ca nhiá»…m cao v&amp;agrave; tÄƒng nhanh, xuáº¥t hiá»‡n nhiá»u á»• dá»‹ch tá»‘c Ä‘á»™ l&amp;acirc;y nhiá»…m cao, chÆ°a r&amp;otilde; nguá»“n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Máº¡nh T&amp;ugrave;ng - Há»¯u C&amp;ocirc;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'pho-chu-tich-tp-hcm-thanh-pho-van-tiep-tuc-chi-thi-10', './uploads/images/1624899487_duonganhduc-1624887035-1367-1624887163.jpg', 1, 89, '2021-06-28 23:58:07', '2021-07-07 07:40:27');
