 Ä‘&amp;agrave;n, áº£o thuáº­t... Th&amp;ocirc;ng qua chÆ°Æ¡ng tr&amp;igrave;nh, c&amp;aacute;c em Ä‘á»u muá»‘n g&amp;oacute;p má»™t pháº§n c&amp;ocirc;ng sá»©c nhá» b&amp;eacute; Ä‘á»ƒ c&amp;ugrave;ng vá»›i qu&amp;ecirc; hÆ°Æ¡ng Viá»‡t Nam Ä‘áº©y l&amp;ugrave;i Ä‘áº¡i dá»‹ch.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;Táº¥m l&amp;ograve;ng cá»§a nhá»¯ng em b&amp;eacute; mang d&amp;ograve;ng m&amp;aacute;u Viá»‡t cÅ©ng l&amp;agrave;m lay Ä‘á»™ng tr&amp;aacute;i tim cá»§a ngÆ°á»i lá»›n, nháº¯c nhá»Ÿ ch&amp;uacute;ng ta vá» truyá»n thá»‘ng &amp;quot;c&amp;acirc;y c&amp;oacute; cá»™i, suá»‘i c&amp;oacute; nguá»“n&amp;quot;, chá»‹ n&amp;oacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nhá»¯ng bá»©c tranh cá»§a c&amp;aacute;c em b&amp;eacute; gá»‘c Viá»‡t gá»­i vá» chÆ°Æ¡ng tr&amp;igrave;nh Talents Show sáº½ Ä‘Æ°á»£c tá»• chá»©c Ä‘áº¥u gi&amp;aacute; trá»±c tiáº¿p tr&amp;ecirc;n page cá»§a chiáº¿n dá»‹ch. Nh&amp;agrave; t&amp;agrave;i trá»£ Ä‘Æ°a ra má»©c gi&amp;aacute; cho sáº£n pháº©m muá»‘n mua á»Ÿ trong má»¥c comment má»—i áº£nh sáº£n pháº©m. Tá»« ng&amp;agrave;y 28/6, ban tá»• chá»©c sáº½ káº¿t ná»‘i nh&amp;agrave; t&amp;agrave;i trá»£ c&amp;oacute; má»©c gi&amp;aacute; cao nháº¥t vá»›i t&amp;aacute;c giáº£/ngÆ°á»i Ä‘áº¡i diá»‡n qua Facebook Ä‘á»ƒ thá»±c hiá»‡n viá»‡c chuyá»ƒn khoáº£n v&amp;agrave; chuyá»ƒn ph&amp;aacute;t sáº£n pháº©m. To&amp;agrave;n bá»™ sá»‘ tiá»n Ä‘áº¥u gi&amp;aacute; sáº½ Ä‘Æ°á»£c chuyá»ƒn tá»›i Quá»¹ Vaccine ph&amp;ograve;ng COVID-19 Viá»‡t Nam (VFVC).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/06/25/tranh-chien-dich-vaccine-edite-2280-6072-1624622083.jpg?w=1020&amp;amp;h=0&amp;amp;q=100&amp;amp;dpr=1&amp;amp;fit=crop&amp;amp;s=eZ8laMoEVgDYpl4BFzGcZA&quot; style=&quot;height:672px; width:500px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Chiáº¿n dá»‹ch &amp;quot;10.000 liá»u vaccine ph&amp;ograve;ng Covid-19 cho Viá»‡t Nam&amp;quot; Ä‘Æ°á»£c nh&amp;oacute;m Chung tay v&amp;igrave