(12, 1, 20, 'Harrison Ford bá»‹ thÆ°Æ¡ng khi quay \"Indiana Jones 5\"', '&lt;p&gt;T&amp;agrave;i tá»­ Harrison Ford gáº·p cháº¥n thÆ°Æ¡ng á»Ÿ vai tr&amp;ecirc;n phim trÆ°á»ng &amp;quot;Indiana Jones 5&amp;quot; v&amp;agrave; sáº½ pháº£i nghá»‰ ngÆ¡i má»™t thá»i gian.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ng&amp;agrave;y 23/6, nguá»“n tin cá»§a&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Variety&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;cho biáº¿t: &amp;quot;Trong má»™t buá»•i táº­p cáº£nh chiáº¿n Ä‘áº¥u, Harrison Ford d&amp;iacute;nh cháº¥n thÆ°Æ¡ng á»Ÿ vai. C&amp;ocirc;ng viá»‡c sáº£n xuáº¥t phim váº«n diá»…n ra song song qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh Ä‘iá»u trá»‹. Trong v&amp;agrave;i tuáº§n tá»›i, &amp;ecirc;-k&amp;iacute;p sáº½ Ä‘iá»u chá»‰nh lá»‹ch quay Ä‘á»ƒ thá»±c hiá»‡n c&amp;aacute;c cáº£nh kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; Ford tham gia trÆ°á»›c&amp;quot;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Harrison Ford trong vai Indiana Jones&quot; src=&quot;https://i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net/2021/06/24/Indiana-Jones-4165-1624529188.jpg?w=680&amp;amp;h=0&amp;amp;q=100&amp;amp;dpr=1&amp;amp;fit=crop&amp;amp;s=xu2ALS-0ro_p8bl8IvmPNQ&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;Harrison Ford trong vai Indiana Jones. áº¢nh:&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Disney&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Äo&amp;agrave;n phim kh&amp;ocirc;ng tiáº¿t lá»™ má»©c Ä‘á»™ nghi&amp;ecirc;m trá»ng cá»§a váº¿t thÆ°Æ¡ng. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, Ford dá»± kiáº¿n pháº£i nghá»‰ v&amp;agrave;i tuáº§n. Nam diá»…n vi&amp;ecirc;n nhiá»u láº§n gáº·p tai náº¡n trong sá»± nghiá»‡p Ä‘&amp;oacute;ng phim h&amp;agrave;nh Ä‘á»™ng. Äáº§u tháº­p ni&amp;ecirc;n 1980, Ford bá»‹ thÆ°Æ¡ng náº·ng á»Ÿ lÆ°ng khi quay&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Indiana Jones and The Temple of Doom&lt;/em&gt;. &amp;Ocirc;ng cÅ©ng bá»‹ cháº¥n thÆ°Æ¡ng ch&amp;acirc;n khi Ä‘&amp;oacute;ng&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;Star Wars: The Force Awakens&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;(2015).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Dá»± 