(17, 1, 6, 'TP HCM láº¥y Ã½ kiáº¿n phá»¥ huynh vá» phÆ°Æ¡ng Ã¡n thi tá»‘t nghiá»‡p', '&lt;p&gt;Äáº¿n 19h ng&amp;agrave;y 28/6, hÆ¡n 89.200 phá»¥ huynh á»Ÿ TP HCM sáº½ ho&amp;agrave;n táº¥t viá»‡c Ä‘Æ°a ra &amp;yacute; kiáº¿n c&amp;oacute; hay kh&amp;ocirc;ng Ä‘á»“ng &amp;yacute; cho con thi tá»‘t nghiá»‡p THPT Ä‘á»£t 1 ng&amp;agrave;y 7-8/7.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Chiá»u 28/6, phiáº¿u kháº£o s&amp;aacute;t láº¥y &amp;yacute; kiáº¿n phá»¥ huynh Ä‘Æ°á»£c Sá»Ÿ Gi&amp;aacute;o dá»¥c v&amp;agrave; Ä&amp;agrave;o táº¡o ph&amp;aacute;t Ä‘i vá»›i 3 lá»±a chá»n:&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;y&amp;ecirc;n t&amp;acirc;m v&amp;agrave; Ä‘á»“ng &amp;yacute;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;cho con&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://vnexpress.net/chu-de/thi-tot-nghiep-thpt-2021-3336&quot; rel=&quot;dofollow&quot;&gt;thi tá»‘t nghiá»‡p THPT nÄƒm 2021&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;Ä‘á»£t 1;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;kh&amp;ocirc;ng y&amp;ecirc;n t&amp;acirc;m nhÆ°ng váº«n Ä‘á»“ng &amp;yacute;;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;kh&amp;ocirc;ng y&amp;ecirc;n t&amp;acirc;m v&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng Ä‘á»“ng &amp;yacute;&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Äá»™ng th&amp;aacute;i n&amp;agrave;y Ä‘Æ°á»£c Ä‘Æ°a ra Ä‘á»ƒ Sá»Ÿ c&amp;oacute; cÆ¡ sá»Ÿ xem x&amp;eacute;t to&amp;agrave;n diá»‡n khi quyáº¿t Ä‘á»‹nh tá»• chá»©c thi tá»‘t nghiá»‡p THPT, tr&amp;aacute;nh g&amp;acirc;y t&amp;acirc;m l&amp;yacute; hoang mang, lo láº¯ng, áº£nh hÆ°á»Ÿng Ä‘áº¿n káº¿t quáº£ thi cá»§a th&amp;iacute; sinh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c trÆ°á»ng c&amp;oacute; thá»ƒ láº¥y &amp;yacute; kiáº¿n phá»¥ huynh hoáº·c ngÆ°á»i gi&amp;aacute;m há»™ há»c sinh qua c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;oacute;m cá»§a lá»›p há»c, Google Form rá»“i tá»•ng há»£p, b&amp;aacute;o c&amp;aacute;o Sá»Ÿ.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&amp;aacute;ng c&amp;ugrave;ng ng&amp;agrave;y, UBND TP HCM há»p Ban chá»‰ Ä‘áº¡o ph&amp;ograve;ng chá»‘ng Covid-19, thá»‘ng nháº¥t sáº½ quyáº¿t Ä‘á»‹nh phÆ°Æ¡ng &amp;aacute;n thi tá»‘t nghiá»‡p THPT v&amp;agrave;o ng&amp;agrave;y 30/6 - ng&amp;a