(22, 7, 3, 'Má»¹ vÃ  Ukraine táº­p tráº­n háº£i quÃ¢n thÆ°á»ng niÃªn trÃªn Biá»ƒn Äen', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TÆ° lá»‡nh háº£i qu&amp;acirc;n Ukraine Oleksiy Neizhpapa cho biáº¿t cuá»™c táº­p tráº­n nháº±m ph&amp;aacute;t Ä‘i th&amp;ocirc;ng Ä‘iá»‡p vá» duy tr&amp;igrave; sá»± á»•n Ä‘á»‹nh v&amp;agrave; h&amp;ograve;a b&amp;igrave;nh trong khu vá»±c.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://cdnimg.vietnamplus.vn/uploaded/pcfo/2021_06_29/ttxvn_2906_bien_den.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;My va Ukraine tap tran hai quan thuong nien tren Bien Den hinh anh 1&quot; src=&quot;https://cdnimg.vietnamplus.vn/t620/uploaded/pcfo/2021_06_29/ttxvn_2906_bien_den.jpg&quot; title=&quot;Má»¹ v&agrave; Ukraine táº­p tráº­n háº£i qu&acirc;n thÆ°á»ng ni&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n Biá»ƒn Äen h&igrave;nh áº£nh 1&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px&quot;&gt;T&amp;agrave;u khu trá»¥c trang bá»‹ t&amp;ecirc;n lá»­a dáº«n Ä‘Æ°á»ng cá»§a Má»¹ USS Ross. (áº¢nh: AFP/TTXVN)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ng&amp;agrave;y 28/6, Má»¹ v&amp;agrave; Ukraine Ä‘&amp;atilde; báº¯t Ä‘áº§u cuá»™c&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.vietnamplus.vn/tags/t%e1%ba%adp-tr%e1%ba%adn-h%e1%ba%a3i-qu%c3%a2n.vnp&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;táº­p tráº­n háº£i qu&amp;acirc;n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;Ä‘a phÆ°Æ¡ng thÆ°á»ng ni&amp;ecirc;n Sea Breeze (Gi&amp;oacute; biá»ƒn) 2021 táº¡i Biá»ƒn Äen.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&amp;aacute;t biá»ƒu trong lá»… khai máº¡c táº¡i th&amp;agrave;nh phá»‘ Odessa (Ukraine), TÆ° lá»‡nh háº£i qu&amp;acirc;n Ukraine Oleksiy Neizhpapa cho biáº¿t cuá»™c táº­p tráº­n nháº±m ph&amp;aacute;t Ä‘i th&amp;ocirc;ng Ä‘iá»‡p vá» duy tr&amp;igrave; sá»± á»•n Ä‘á»‹nh v&amp;agrave; h&amp;ograve;a b&amp;igrave;nh trong khu vá»±c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c cuá»™c táº­p tráº­n Sea Breeze Ä‘&amp;atilde; diá»…n ra 21 láº§n ká»ƒ tá»« nÄƒm 19