(31, 1, 19, 'BÃ³ng Ä‘Ã¡ lÃ m chÃ­nh trá»‹', '&lt;p&gt;Trong khu&amp;ocirc;n khá»•&lt;a href=&quot;https://thanhnien.vn/the-thao/euro-2020/&quot; rel=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;giáº£i v&amp;ocirc; Ä‘á»‹ch b&amp;oacute;ng Ä‘&amp;aacute; ch&amp;acirc;u &amp;Acirc;u&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;Ä‘ang diá»…n ra, c&amp;oacute; láº½ kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; tráº­n Ä‘áº¥u n&amp;agrave;o m&amp;agrave; &amp;yacute; nghÄ©a v&amp;agrave; t&amp;aacute;c Ä‘á»™ng cá»§a n&amp;oacute; vÆ°á»£t háº³n ra ngo&amp;agrave;i phÆ°Æ¡ng diá»‡n&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://thanhnien.vn/the-thao/&quot; rel=&quot;&quot;&gt;thá»ƒ thao&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;nhÆ° tráº­n Anh - Äá»©c á»Ÿ thá»§ Ä‘&amp;ocirc; London (Anh) vá»«a qua.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:void();&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Tiá»n Ä‘áº¡o Ä‘á»™i Anh ghi b&agrave;n quyáº¿t Ä‘á»‹nh trong tráº­n tháº¯ng Äá»©c táº¡i Euro 2020 /// Reuters&quot; src=&quot;https://image.thanhnien.vn/2048/uploaded/hoangnam/2021_07_02/kane_sitw.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:312px; width:500px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;Tiá»n Ä‘áº¡o Ä‘á»™i Anh ghi b&amp;agrave;n quyáº¿t Ä‘á»‹nh trong tráº­n tháº¯ng Äá»©c táº¡i Euro 2020&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;REUTERS&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Káº¿t quáº£ Anh tháº¯ng vá»›i tá»· sá»‘ 2-0. NÆ°á»›c Anh pháº¥n kh&amp;iacute;ch bá»Ÿi láº§n Ä‘áº§u ti&amp;ecirc;n ká»ƒ tá»« tráº­n tháº¯ng Ä‘á»™i tuyá»ƒn Äá»©c Ä‘á»ƒ gi&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;uacute;p v&amp;ocirc; Ä‘á»‹ch&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://thanhnien.vn/the-gioi/&quot; rel=&quot;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;tháº¿ giá»›i&amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;nÄƒm 1966, th&amp;igrave; nay má»›i láº¡i Ä‘&amp;aacute;nh báº¡i Ä‘á»™i tuyá»ƒn Äá»©c trong v&amp;ograve;ng Ä‘áº¥u loáº¡i trá»±c tiáº¿p á»Ÿ c&amp;aacute;c&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://thethao.thanhnien.vn/bong-da-quoc-te/&quot; rel=&quot;&quot;&gt;giáº£i v&amp;ocirc; Ä‘á»‹ch b&am