sá»­ dá»¥ng trong trÆ°á»ng há»£p kháº©n cáº¥p, cáº§n t&amp;iacute;nh lÆ°u Ä‘á»™ng cao. Táº¡i c&amp;aacute;c khu c&amp;aacute;ch ly, s&amp;aacute;ng kiáº¿n n&amp;agrave;y ph&amp;aacute;t huy t&amp;aacute;c dá»¥ng cao khi cung cáº¥p chá»— ngá»§ nghá»‰ vá»‡ sinh, tiá»‡n lá»£i cho h&amp;agrave;ng ng&amp;agrave;n ngÆ°á»i, trong khi tiáº¿t kiá»‡m chi ph&amp;iacute; v&amp;agrave; thá»i gian láº¯p Ä‘áº·t. Trong Ä‘á»£t b&amp;ugrave;ng ph&amp;aacute;t Covid-19 táº¡i Báº¯c Giang v&amp;agrave; Háº£i DÆ°Æ¡ng, giÆ°á»ng giáº¥y Ä‘&amp;atilde; Ä‘Æ°á»£c sá»­ dá»¥ng hiá»‡u quáº£. V&amp;igrave; váº­y, SOVI v&amp;agrave; SCGP Ä‘&amp;atilde; tiáº¿p tá»¥c mang s&amp;aacute;ng kiáº¿n &amp;yacute; nghÄ©a n&amp;agrave;y Ä‘áº¿n vá»›i c&amp;aacute;c &amp;ldquo;Ä‘iá»ƒm n&amp;oacute;ng&amp;rdquo; táº¡i TP.HCM.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;table align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;GiÆ°á»ng giáº¥y SCGP vá»›i thiáº¿t káº¿ hÆ°á»›ng Ä‘áº¿n ph&aacute;t triá»ƒn bá»n vá»¯ng nhÆ°ng váº«n Ä‘áº£m báº£o t&iacute;nh linh hoáº¡t cao&quot; src=&quot;https://image.thanhnien.vn/2048/uploaded/linhnt.qc/2021_07_07/scgp/scgp_3_megd.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:568px; width:500px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;GiÆ°á»ng giáº¥y SCGP vá»›i thiáº¿t káº¿ hÆ°á»›ng Ä‘áº¿n ph&amp;aacute;t triá»ƒn bá»n vá»¯ng nhÆ°ng váº«n Ä‘áº£m báº£o t&amp;iacute;nh linh hoáº¡t cao&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;table align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Nhá»¯ng chiáº¿c xe chuy&ecirc;n chá»Ÿ giÆ°á»ng giáº¥y ká»‹p thá»i há»— trá»£ c&aacute;c Ä‘iá»ƒm n&oacute;ng cá»§a TP.HCM ngay trong Ä‘&ecirc;m&quot; src=&quot;https://image.thanhnien.vn/2048/uploaded