\r\n&lt;table align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;B&aacute;c báº£o vá»‡ Äƒn xin giá»¯a dá»‹ch Covid-19: &lsquo;Cáº£m Æ¡n sá»± tá»­ táº¿ cá»§a ngÆ°á»i S&agrave;i G&ograve;n&rsquo; - áº£nh 3&quot; src=&quot;https://image.thanhnien.vn/2048/uploaded/thanhthuy/2021_07_06/anh4_ygqy.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:353px; width:500px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;Vá»£ chá»“ng &amp;ocirc;ng Vinh Ä‘á»u kh&amp;ocirc;ng giáº¥u Ä‘Æ°á»£c niá»m vui v&amp;igrave; nhá»¯ng ng&amp;agrave;y qua nháº­n Ä‘Æ°á»£c sá»± quan t&amp;acirc;m, y&amp;ecirc;u thÆ°Æ¡ng cá»§a qu&amp;aacute; nhiá»u ngÆ°á»i&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;áº¢NH: CAO AN BI&amp;Ecirc;N&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong cÄƒn trá» nhá» Ä‘&amp;atilde; tá»« ráº¥t l&amp;acirc;u ngá»¥p láº·n trong ná»—i lo &amp;ldquo;cÆ¡m, &amp;aacute;o, gáº¡o, tiá»n&amp;rdquo;, nay bá»—ng bá»«ng s&amp;aacute;ng háº³n bá»Ÿi tiáº¿ng cÆ°á»i. Táº¥t cáº£ Ä‘á»u nhá» sá»± tá»­ táº¿ &amp;ldquo;qu&amp;aacute; má»©c&amp;rdquo; cá»§a ngÆ°á»i S&amp;agrave;i G&amp;ograve;n vá»‘n tá»« báº¥y l&amp;acirc;u nay váº«n váº­y&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Chia sáº» vá»›i PV&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;Thanh Ni&amp;ecirc;n&lt;/em&gt;, chá»‹ Nguyá»…n Äá»— Tr&amp;uacute;c PhÆ°Æ¡ng cho biáº¿t chá»‹ Ä‘&amp;atilde; nháº­n quy&amp;ecirc;n g&amp;oacute;p ri&amp;ecirc;ng cho ho&amp;agrave;n cáº£nh cá»§a &amp;ocirc;ng Vinh v&amp;agrave; Ä‘Æ°á»£c máº¡nh thÆ°á»ng qu&amp;acirc;n á»§ng há»™ sá»‘ tiá»n 200 triá»‡u Ä‘á»“ng. V&amp;igrave; l&amp;agrave; sá»‘ tiá»n lá»›n, chá»‹ tr&amp;iacute;ch tiá»n gá»­i cho &amp;ocirc;ng Vinh 150 triá»‡u Ä‘á»“ng trong Ä‘&amp;oacute; 120 triá»‡u Ä‘á»“ng v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;agrave;i khoáº£n tiáº¿t kiá»‡m v&amp;agrave; 30 triá»‡u Ä‘á»“ng v&amp;agrave;o tháº» ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng, 50 triá»‡u c&amp;ograve;n láº¡i Ä‘á»ƒ v&amp;agrave;o quá»¹ chung Ä‘á»ƒ gi&amp;uacute;p Ä‘á»¡ nhá»¯ng&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://thanhnien.vn/doi-song/cong-dong/&quot; rel=&quot;&quot;&gt;ho&amp;agrave;n cáº£nh kh&amp;oacute; khÄƒn&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;kh&amp;aacute;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tá»«ng gi&amp;uacute;p qua nhiá»u ho&amp;agrave;n cáº£nh nhÆ°ng ho&amp;agrave;n cáº£nh cá»§a &amp;ocirc;ng Vinh khiáº¿n chá»‹ PhÆ°Æ¡ng x&amp;uacute;c Ä‘á»™ng khi &amp;ocirc;ng hai láº§n báº­t kh&amp;oacute;c. Láº§n Ä‘áº§u ti&amp;ecirc;n khi chá»‹ Ä‘áº¿n gáº·p &amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave; láº§n thá»© hai l&amp;agrave; &amp;ocirc;ng bÆ°á»›c ra khá»i ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng sau khi l&amp;agrave;m tháº» tiáº¿t kiá»‡m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Nhá»¯ng ngÆ°á»i lá»›n tuá»•i thÆ°á»ng l&amp;ograve;ng tá»± trá»ng cá»§a ngÆ°á»i ta ráº¥t cao, váº­y m&amp;agrave; v&amp;igrave; vá»£ v&amp;agrave; c&amp;ograve;n tr&amp;aacute;ch nhiá»‡m cá»§a má»™t ngÆ°á»i Ä‘&amp;agrave;n &amp;ocirc;ng n&amp;ecirc;n cháº¥p nháº­n ra Ä‘Æ°á»ng Ä‘á»ƒ xin Äƒn nhÆ° váº­y khiáº¿n t&amp;ocirc;i nghÄ© m&amp;igrave;nh n&amp;ecirc;n gi&amp;uacute;p Ä‘á»¡ ch&amp;uacute;. Ch&amp;uacute; Ä‘&amp;atilde; kh&amp;oacute; b&amp;agrave;y tá» ráº±ng chÆ°a bao giá» trong Ä‘á»i ch&amp;uacute; c&amp;oacute; má»™t sá»‘ tiá»n lá»›n nhÆ° tháº¿&amp;rdquo;, chá»‹ n&amp;oacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, viá»‡c quy&amp;ecirc;n g&amp;oacute;p má»™t sá»‘ tiá»n lá»›n khiáº¿n nhiá»u cá»™ng Ä‘á»“ng máº¡ng tranh c&amp;atilde;i khi cho ráº±ng sá»‘ tiá»n 150 triá»‡u Ä‘á»“ng l&amp;agrave; qu&amp;aacute; nhiá»u trong khi c&amp;ograve;n nhiá»u ho&amp;agrave;n cáº£nh kh&amp;aacute;c kh&amp;oacute; khÄƒn hÆ¡n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;TrÆ°á»›c sá»± tranh c&amp;atilde;i n&amp;agrave;y, chá»‹ PhÆ°Æ¡ng váº«n b&amp;igrave;nh tÄ©nh giáº£i th&amp;iacute;ch tr&amp;ecirc;n trang c&amp;aacute; nh&amp;acirc;n, chá»‹ t&amp;acirc;m sá»± trÆ°á»›c Ä‘&amp;acirc;y c&amp;oacute; nhá»¯ng trÆ°á»ng há»£p chá»‹ trao Ä‘áº¿n h